- **Check field kind:** `if (field.kind === 'scalar') { ... }`

### Step 3: Build FileMap instead of writing directly
```typescript
const fileMap = {
  'index.ts': '// index',
  'api': {
    'users.ts': '// users endpoints',
    'posts.ts': '// posts endpoints'
  }
}
```

Prisma CLI automatically converts FileMap to actual files on disk.

---

## **File Locations Summary**

| Purpose | File |
|---------|------|
| Generator Handler | `/packages/generator-helper/src/generatorHandler.ts` |
| Generator Interfaces | `/packages/generator/src/generator.ts` + `configuration.ts` |
| DMMF Type Definitions | `/packages/dmmf/src/dmmf.ts` |
| Real Example (TS) | `/packages/client-generator-ts/src/generator.ts` + `generateClient.ts` |
| Model/Field Processing | `/packages/client-generator-ts/src/TSClient/Output.ts` |
| Enum Processing | `/packages/client-generator-ts/src/TSClient/Enum.ts` |
| Test Example | `/packages/generator-helper/src/__tests__/minimal-executable` |

---

This should give you everything needed to build your REST API client generator!

